text: Lah may refer to: *Lah (surname) * Lithium aluminium hydride * Lah, Victoria, a locality in Australia * Lah, Kona, a village in Kona Department, Mouhoun Province, Burkina Faso * Lah, Yaba, a village in Yaba Department, Nayala Province, Burkina Faso * A Singlish/Manglish term used for emphasis or reassurance
title: Lah
